    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless E92 M3, a high-revving masterclass in atmospheric induction. This specimen features the legendary S65 V8, with critical preventative maintenance\u2014including rod bearing replacement and reinforced throttle actuators\u2014already executed to exacting tolerances. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast gear synchronization, while the EDC-equipped suspension provides surgical damping control. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with zero subframe deflection, and the factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster consistent with climate-controlled storage. This is a turnkey, collector-grade apex hunter optimized for peak volumetric efficiency.",
